<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url('https://www.rd.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/03-healthy-lunch-break-packed-lunch.jpg');">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>
      <span id="banner-typed-text" class="banner-area"></span>
    </h1>
    <h1>Pra quem quer pagar <strong>pouco</strong> e ainda <strong>ajudar o planeta</strong>!</h1>
    <p>Mude seus hábitos e venha conhecer o melhor que os restaurantes próximos tem a oferecer</p>

    <h1>Busque sua próxima refeição:</h1>
    <div class="my-4">
      <%= simple_form_for :search, url: dishes_path, method: :get do |f| %>
        <div class="search-form-control form-group">
          <input class="form-control string required" type="text" name="address" id="search_query" />
          <button name="button" type="submit" class="btn btn-flat">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i> Search
          </button>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="list-buttons d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
      <%= link_to "Lanche", dishes_path({category: "Lanche"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      <%= link_to "Marmita", dishes_path({category: "Marmita"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      <%= link_to "Japonesa", dishes_path({category: "Japonesa"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      <%= link_to "Pizza", dishes_path({category: "Pizza"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      <%= link_to "Padaria", dishes_path({category: "Padaria"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      <%= link_to "Árabe", dishes_path({category: "Árabe"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
      <%= link_to "Chinesa", dishes_path({category: "Chinesa"}), class: "btn btn-flat" %>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-5">Quer ser parceiro Sobrou? <span> <%= link_to "Cadastre seu Restaurante", new_restaurant_path, class:"btn-ghost" %> </span> </p>
    <h1 class= "mt-5">Confira no mapa abaixo os restaurantes cadastrados perto de você:</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="map"
   style="width: 100%; height: 600px;"
   data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
   data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
</div>
